  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的凭证签发流程，从秘书登录开始，一直到文档最终备份到云端。这个流程要体现自动化备份和云同步的机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Secretary",
        "User Interface",
        "AuthService",
        "BackupService",
        "CloudSyncService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到了秘书作为用户角色，还有认证服务。我想确认一下，登录流程里秘书是直接和界面交互，然后界面再调用AuthService来验证用户名密码，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Secretary",
        "User Interface",
        "AuthService",
        "credentials",
        "username",
        "password"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，秘书在UI上输入用户名密码，UI把凭证传给AuthService做认证，认证结果返回给UI，成功后再通知秘书登录成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Secretary",
        "User Interface",
        "AuthService",
        "credentials",
        "auth result"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，登录部分我先画好了。接下来是签发环节，秘书录入申请信息后，UI应该调用哪个服务来创建签发记录？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Secretary",
        "User Interface",
        "IssuanceService",
        "data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里需要IssuanceService来统一处理。秘书在UI上录入请求人信息、凭证类型和用途后，UI把data传给IssuanceService创建签发记录。然后IssuanceService要调用PdfService生成PDF草稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Secretary",
        "User Interface",
        "IssuanceService",
        "PdfService",
        "issuance draft",
        "data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
